Third-party components

The full list of third-party Go and JavaScript dependencies, with
their respective licences, can be reproduced via:

  go mod download -json all          # for Go modules
  pnpm licenses list                 # for pnpm-managed JS packages

No third-party licence text is bundled in this repository directly;
licences are governed by the upstream packages and downloaded as part
of the build.
